This is a placeholder for the Windows/Linux icon file.

To create a proper icon:

1. Design a 1024x1024 PNG icon (see ICON_DESIGN.md for guidelines)
2. Replace this file with your icon

For Windows (.ico), you can use:
- https://cloudconvert.com/png-to-ico
- https://convertio.co/png-ico/

For Linux, PNG is sufficient.
